Comment: Reti. I intend on the Fianchetto at this point, but what I like about f3 is there are so many options. I've learned this is probably not a good opening when I'm playing a more advanced player.
Book
I have had some success against 1300-1400 level players when I Fianchetto and that is still my plan. I prefer flank attacks.
